Ihe i kwesịrị ị maka Bishop Peter Okpaleke emere 'Cardinal'
Bịshọpụ Okpaleke so na ndị isi ụka mmadụ 21 Poopụ Francis kwupụtara aha ha taa bụ ụbọchịụka na a ga-ete mmanụ ịbụ Cardinal n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ, 2022.

Cheta na aha Okpaleke malitere wuwe na Naijiria niile dịka ndị ụkọchụkwu na ndị ụka Katọlik na Ahiara Dayọsis jụrụ ịnabata nhọpụta a họpụtara ya dịka Bịshọpụ n'afọ 2012 mana e mechara mee ya Bishopụ Ekwulobia.

Ije OKpaleke dịka ụkọchukwu malitere na mberede dịka a kpọrọ ya gbaa odibo n'ofufe nro mbụ ya n'amụghị ya amụ  otu ụbọchịụka dịka ndị na-agba odibo n'ọlta nke a na-akpọ "mass servers" abaghị ụka n'ihi mmiri ozizo.

Okpalaeke etinyela akwụkwọ arụkwaghịm
Ndị ụka katọlịk emeela ngagharị maka nchekwa ndụ na Naijirịa
A mụrụ Ọkpaleke  n'abalị Mbụ nke ọnwa Maachị 1, afọ 1963.
Onye Amesi dị n'Okpuru Ọchịchị Aguata, Nne na nna ya bụ Reuben Ezeuko Okpaleke na Bridget Ekejimma Okpaleke.
Mana Bishopu Ọkpaleke toro n'Ụga n'aka nnenne ya bụ Evelyn Abiahuaku Ibekwe bụ ebe o gara Oganiru Primary School  na Uga Boys' Secondary School.

Ọ gara seminary na St. John Bosco Seminary Isuaniocha, Bigard Memorial Seminary bụ nke a ma ugbua dịka St. Joseph's Major Seminary Ikot-Ekpene, Catholic Institute of West Africa (CIWA), Port Harcourt na mahadum 'Pontificia Universita Della Santa Croce, Rome, Italy' bụ ebe o nwetara "first class" bụ ebe o nwere na "Canon Law" in First Class Honours.
E chiri ya ụkọchukwu  n'abalị 22 nnke afọ 1992.
Ọ rụọla dịka ụkọchukwu na-achịkọta St. Anthony's parish Nanka, Ss. John and Paul Umubele Awka na St. Joseph the Worker Chaplaincy, Nnamdi Azikiwe University Awka.
